::-> Transaction fee calculation ?

Ans:  Transaction Fee=(Gas Consumed * Gas Price) * (Ether Price / 10^9)

Note -> 1 ether = 10^9 wei 

https://sepolia.etherscan.io/tx/0xdcb3f3909c28914b3aded9b04f6290bf4ff09e4d25e4061fa05dbaa1e92b0104

Gas Price:  18.796262962 Gwei (0.000000018796262962 ETH)

Gas Limit & Usage by Txn:  26,750 | 26,407 (98.72%)

